# LAMMPS Input File  (figure: solid-liquid interface evolution vs temperature)
# Licensed under CC BY 4.0
# Build ONE solid-liquid two-phase cell of fcc Al (Mendelev potential), then
# hold a copy of it at three temperatures -- above, at, and below the melting
# point -- and snapshot the interface at four times each.  Below Tm the solid
# (right) grows into the liquid (left); above Tm it melts; near Tm it barely
# moves.  Atoms are colored by common-neighbor analysis of the INHERENT
# structure (a brief minimization per snapshot removes thermal noise, since
# near Tm the instantaneous structures of hot solid and liquid overlap).
#
# Designed to run in parallel (e.g. mpirun -np 64 lmp -in evolution.lmp).
# The three temperatures may need a few-kelvin adjustment to straddle this
# cell's Tm; the segment length (run NNN) sets how far the interface moves
# between frames.  Assemble the 12 PNGs with, e.g.:
#   montage evo_970_*.png evo_930_*.png evo_890_*.png -tile 4x3 -geometry +4+4 evolution.png

# ---------- build the two-phase cell ----------
units metal
atom_style atomic
boundary p p p
lattice fcc 4.05
region box block 0 10 0 10 0 40          # bigger cross-section for a clean interface
create_box 1 box
create_atoms 1 box
mass 1 26.98
pair_style eam/fs
pair_coeff * * ../Al_mm.eam.fs Al
velocity all create 800.0 7654 mom yes rot yes
timestep 0.002
thermo 10000

fix eq all npt temp 800.0 800.0 0.2 x 0 0 2 y 0 0 2 z 0 0 2 couple xy
run 15000
unfix eq
variable zmid equal zlo+(zhi-zlo)/2.0
region rtop block INF INF INF INF ${zmid} INF units box
group top region rtop
group bot subtract all top
fix baro all nph z 0 0 2
fix hot  top langevin 1400.0 1400.0 0.1 11111
fix cold bot langevin  800.0  800.0 0.1 22222
run 20000
unfix hot
unfix cold
write_restart start.restart

# ---------- evolve at three temperatures, saving 4 snapshots each ----------
variable T index 970 930 890             # above / near / below Tm (tune to cell)
label tloop
clear
read_restart start.restart
pair_style eam/fs
pair_coeff * * ../Al_mm.eam.fs Al
timestep 0.002
reset_timestep 0
fix baro all nph x 0 0 2 y 0 0 2 z 0 0 2 couple xy
fix th all langevin $T $T 0.1 4321
thermo 10000
write_restart evo_$T_0.restart
run 30000
write_restart evo_$T_1.restart
run 30000
write_restart evo_$T_2.restart
run 30000
write_restart evo_$T_3.restart
next T
jump SELF tloop

# ---------- render the 12 snapshots (inherent structure, z horizontal) ----------
variable S index evo_970_0 evo_970_1 evo_970_2 evo_970_3 &
                 evo_930_0 evo_930_1 evo_930_2 evo_930_3 &
                 evo_890_0 evo_890_1 evo_890_2 evo_890_3
label sloop
clear
read_restart ${S}.restart
pair_style eam/fs
pair_coeff * * ../Al_mm.eam.fs Al
minimize 1.0e-6 1.0e-6 2000 20000
compute cna all cna/atom 3.6
thermo_style custom step pe
run 0
# z runs left-right; liquid (low fcc) left, solid (steelblue) right
write_dump all image ${S}.png c_cna type adiam 2.6 &
    view 90 -90 up 1 0 0 zoom 6.2 size 1000 300 shiny 0.15 fsaa yes ssao yes 7123 0.6 &
    box yes 0.02 modify backcolor white boxcolor midnightblue &
    amap 1 5 sa 1.0 5 steelblue purple green red gray
next S
jump SELF sloop
